    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear, including some scratches and minor dents. The interior has noticeable signs of use and age. All major mechanical components are functional, though some parts may require maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. Mechanically, it is sound, starting up reliably and shifting smoothly through all gears with no strange noises or leaks. The interior is clean and comfortable, though you might find some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few minor scuffs on the plastic trim consistent with regular use. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, but there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper that are visible upon close inspection. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for many more miles of service.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive reliability and sophisticated design. This vehicle has been curated to ensure consistent performance and a refined cabin environment, reflecting a history of diligent maintenance. Featuring a well-preserved exterior and a robust powertrain, it offers a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking an optimal balance of quality and value. Thoroughly inspected for operational excellence and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This beauty is in great shape and has been really well-loved. It runs like a dream and looks fantastic inside and out! It's been super dependable for me, and I just know you're going to love how it handles on the road. It's perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This driver-spec example features a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with M-specific geometry and reinforced subframe mounting points, providing the tactile feedback and lateral stability expected of this platform. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the vehicle retains its structural and mechanical excellence, making it a perfect candidate for the discerning enthusiast who values performance-first engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "2018 Sedan. Reliable daily driver. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Mechanically sound. Inspection passed.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior presents beautifully in its original paint, maintaining a high-gloss finish with only minor road-pebble chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the premium seating surfaces show light, natural character creasing but remain firm and free of any punctures or thinning. All electronic systems, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's intervals, with a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. It is a solid, honest car that delivers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and refinement. Meticulously maintained and showing consistent care, it offers a robust mechanical profile complemented by a well-preserved interior. This offering represents an ideal synthesis of performance and long-term value, ensuring a premium ownership experience without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s been well-loved and is still running beautifully, perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that\u2019s ready for many more miles. It's got a little bit of character but is in solid shape overall and has been super dependable for me. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a well-maintained 2003 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car exhibits minor road wear consistent with its age, but mechanically remains a sharp example of the E46 platform\u2019s balanced dynamics.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_8",
